## Microservices Local Development Example

## Ports
AUTH_SERVICE_PORT=3001
USER_SERVICE_PORT=3002
INVOICE_SERVICE_PORT=3003
PORT=3000

## Gateway Service URLs
AUTH_SERVICE_URL=http://localhost:3001
USER_SERVICE_URL=http://localhost:3002
INVOICE_SERVICE_URL=http://localhost:3003

## MongoDB
# Local: mongodb://localhost:27017/invoice-app
MONGODB_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/invoice-app

## Google OAuth
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=replace-with-google-client-id
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=replace-with-google-client-secret

## OpenAI
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-openai-api-key-here

## Session (use a long random string)
SESSION_SECRET=replace-with-random-session-secret

## Client origin + environment
CLIENT_URL=http://localhost:3000
NODE_ENV=development

## Notes
# - Keep the same SESSION_SECRET across all services
# - For production, set NODE_ENV=production and secure cookies (handled automatically)
